    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it's spotless, runs like a dream, and has been kept in pristine condition. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a quick sale so someone else can start enjoying it. It's a total head-turner and ready for its next adventure today!",
