    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This chassis is mechanically flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The factory finish remains immaculate, free of any paint depth inconsistencies, while the interior maintains its original tactile integrity. A true analog masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance, ready for the most discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
