    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and the interior retains its original factory aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized master technicians. It has never seen inclement weather, has zero modifications, and has been driven with the utmost care. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
